---
import Reveal from "../motion/Reveal.astro";
---

<section
  id="experiencia"
  class="relative overflow-hidden bg-[var(--color-dark)] py-24 text-white md:py-32"
>
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(126,217,87,0.09),transparent_30rem)]"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="container relative">
    <div class="grid gap-14 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.1fr] lg:items-end">
      <Reveal>
        <div>
          <p
            class="mb-4 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-white/45"
          >
            Experiencia
          </p>

          <h2
            class="heading text-balance text-5xl font-semibold leading-[0.95] md:text-7xl"
          >
            Después de una semana intensa, el cuerpo también necesita
            mantenimiento.
          </h2>
        </div>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal delay={0.1}>
        <p class="max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-white/65 lg:ml-auto">
          Una experiencia pensada para hombres que buscan bajar la tensión,
          recuperar el cuerpo y sostener una rutina de cuidado personal sin
          excesos ni artificios.
        </p>
      </Reveal>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4">
      <Reveal delay={0.08}>
        <article
          class="group h-full rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-7 transition duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white/[0.06]"
        >
          <span
            class="mb-10 block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-125"
          >
          </span>

          <h3 class="heading text-3xl font-semibold">Descarga muscular</h3>

          <p class="mt-5 leading-7 text-white/60">
            Tratamientos orientados a aliviar tensión acumulada, contracturas y
            fatiga corporal.
          </p>
        </article>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal delay={0.16}>
        <article
          class="group h-full rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-7 transition duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white/[0.06]"
        >
          <span
            class="mb-10 block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-125"
          >
          </span>

          <h3 class="heading text-3xl font-semibold">Descanso mental</h3>

          <p class="mt-5 leading-7 text-white/60">
            Un momento reservado para cortar con el ruido, bajar el ritmo y
            recuperar claridad.
          </p>
        </article>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal delay={0.24}>
        <article
          class="group h-full rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-7 transition duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white/[0.06]"
        >
          <span
            class="mb-10 block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-125"
          >
          </span>

          <h3 class="heading text-3xl font-semibold">Cuidado personal</h3>

          <p class="mt-5 leading-7 text-white/60">
            Servicios estéticos discretos, prolijos y pensados para una imagen
            masculina cuidada.
          </p>
        </article>
      </Reveal>

      <Reveal delay={0.32}>
        <article
          class="group h-full rounded-[1.75rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.04] p-7 transition duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white/[0.06]"
        >
          <span
            class="mb-10 block h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-accent)] transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-125"
          >
          </span>

          <h3 class="heading text-3xl font-semibold">Atención profesional</h3>

          <p class="mt-5 leading-7 text-white/60">
            Cada sesión se adapta a tu cuerpo, tu rutina y el tipo de bienestar
            que estás buscando.
          </p>
        </article>
      </Reveal>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
